tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Was T18 at Canada's Q-School, earning conditional status on the Mackenzie Tour. Made three cuts, with season best coming at The Players Cup in July. After 54 holes was T6 on rounds of 68-69-68. A final-round 76 derailed his chances and finished T25.
tourBios.personal: Favorite course he's played is Shadow Creek...Wants to play St. Andrews...Dream foursome would include his dad, Tiger Woods and Rory McIlroy...Twitter name is @jhunterharrison.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T25th in 2015 at the The Players Cup.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T78th in Par Breakers on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
